@page "/"

<PageTitle>Bienvenido a FacturaPop</PageTitle>

<div class="hero-section text-center">
    <div class="mb-4">
        <span class="badge bg-white text-primary border px-3 py-2 rounded-pill shadow-sm">
            🚀 Gestión inteligente v2.0
        </span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="display-3 mb-3 fw-bold text-dark">
        Facturación <span class="brand-gradient">Pop</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="lead text-muted mb-5 mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
        El sistema que transforma tu contabilidad aburrida en una experiencia fluida.
        Diseñado para emprendedores modernos.
    </p>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <a href="/facturador" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg shadow-lg px-5 py-3">
            <span class="me-2">✨</span> Crear Factura
        </a>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg px-4 py-3">
            Ver Estadísticas
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center px-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="feature-card p-4">
                <div class="icon-box mb-3">📂</div>
                <h5>Historial Seguro</h5>
                <p class="small text-muted mb-3">Tus facturas guardadas y organizadas automáticamente.</p>
                <a href="/facturas" class="btn btn-link text-decoration-none p-0">Consultar &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="feature-card p-4">
                <div class="icon-box mb-3">📈</div>
                <h5>Reportes Visuales</h5>
                <p class="small text-muted mb-3">Entiende tus ingresos con gráficos claros y coloridos.</p>
                <a href="/reportes" class="btn btn-link text-decoration-none p-0">Analizar &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .hero-section {
        padding: 4rem 0;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #f3e8ff 0%, transparent 40%), radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, #e0e7ff 0%, transparent 40%);
    }

    .brand-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pop-dark) 0%, var(--pop-primary) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .feature-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid var(--pop-silver);
        transition: transform 0.3s;
        height: 100%;
        text-align: left;
    }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--pop-primary);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(144, 103, 198, 0.15);
        }

    .icon-box {
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        background: var(--pop-light);
        border-radius: 12px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--pop-primary);
    }
</style>